                            <comment id="16496" author="balex" created="Sun, 19 Feb 2006 08:56:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I agree, this is a good change to make.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Just ensure all authentication mechanisms (*Filters) use the authRequest.setDetails(new WebAuthenticationDetails(false)) to avoid needless HttpSession creation. There is a property on HttpSessionContextIntegrationFilter if users are using concurrent session support and want to force eager creatio of the HttpSession.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
